snippet.title: UNDERCREATOR Trailer - UNDEREVENT 2024
snippet.description:
Make whatever you want, whenever you want, however you want. No strings attached. No grasping at straws. No need to learn programming.
Just you and your imagination, with no limits.

UNDERCREATOR by Sil Games (me!)
Trailer music by SegaSonic101
Inspired by Super Mario Maker

Project Link:
https://gamejolt.com/games/undercreator/813146

This was featured in @UNDEREVENT 2024, which you can watch here:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ho5jkOfUFtY
